sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Order Service
    participant I as Inventory Service
    participant P as Payment Service
    participant S as Shipping Service
    participant EB as Event Bus (Kafka)

    rect rgb(200, 255, 200)
        Note over O,S: Happy Path — Order Fulfillment Saga
        O->>EB: OrderCreatedEvent(orderId=123)
        EB->>I: OrderCreatedEvent
        I->>I: Reserve inventory
        I->>EB: InventoryReservedEvent(orderId=123)
        EB->>P: InventoryReservedEvent
        P->>P: Charge payment
        P->>EB: PaymentProcessedEvent(orderId=123)
        EB->>S: PaymentProcessedEvent
        S->>S: Schedule shipment
        S->>EB: ShipmentScheduledEvent(orderId=123)
        EB->>O: ShipmentScheduledEvent
        O->>O: Order COMPLETED
    end

    rect rgb(255, 200, 200)
        Note over O,S: Sad Path — Payment Failure with Compensation
        O->>EB: OrderCreatedEvent(orderId=456)
        EB->>I: OrderCreatedEvent
        I->>I: Reserve inventory ✓
        I->>EB: InventoryReservedEvent(orderId=456)
        EB->>P: InventoryReservedEvent
        P->>P: Charge payment ✗ FAILED
        P->>EB: PaymentFailedEvent(orderId=456, reason="Insufficient funds")
        EB->>I: PaymentFailedEvent
        Note over I: Compensating transaction
        I->>I: Release inventory reservation
        I->>EB: InventoryReleasedEvent(orderId=456)
        EB->>O: PaymentFailedEvent
        O->>O: Order CANCELLED
    end
